<plot>Spoof comedy series where fictional director Peter De Lane ('Brydon, Rob' (qv)), provides a voice-over commentary for some of the programmes he has directed during his long career in films and television. De Lane shares with the audience amusing anecdotes about the stars of his "work", divulging some interesting personal information in the process.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?151045</url></doc>
